    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Kingsguard》是一款结合了动作和策略的游戏，白天你建设你的王国，夜晚则准备迎接迫在眉睫的危险。你会带领你的王国走向胜利，还是让它陷入黑暗？<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319240/extras/0c782f4459ed71cca7ef3db0c67a14c4.avif?t=1741788664\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319240/extras_big/0c782f4459ed71cca7ef3db0c67a14c4.avif?t=1741788664 width=800 height=174 /></span><br>白天，你建立防御。你建造炮塔和兵营以组建你的军队。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319240/extras/6c9d632506dd071c5f3e0d2e4c10d233.poster.avif?t=1741788664\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319240/extras/6c9d632506dd071c5f3e0d2e4c10d233.webm?t=1741788664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319240/extras/6c9d632506dd071c5f3e0d2e4c10d233.mp4?t=1741788664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>而到了晚上，你必须保卫你的王国。你可以让炮塔为你而战，也可以率领你的军队出征，甚至亲自上战场作战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319240/extras/7f28d95160f40ffd508b0d930b6795ce.poster.avif?t=1741788664\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319240/extras/7f28d95160f40ffd508b0d930b6795ce.webm?t=1741788664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319240/extras/7f28d95160f40ffd508b0d930b6795ce.mp4?t=1741788664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
